message.raw:
Fixed RFBlaster manual mode

The manual mode, including remote_value_checking now works correctly. Specifically I have added some (sort of hacky) code to make the enable/disable (gate) button work even through the RFBlaster does not have a gate as such (thought setting amplitude to 0 acts as a gate as far as I'm aware)
